==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yeomanly
<hw>Yeo"man*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to a yeoman; becoming
or suitable to, a yeoman; yeomanlike.</def> <rj><au>B.
Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Well could he dress his tackle <qex>yeomanly</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yeomanry</ent>⟦br⟧
